                        "text_blocks": [
                            {
                                "start": 332.613,
                                "stop": 334.832,
                                "byte_start": 1404483,
                                "byte_stop": 1413364,
                                "text": "You are talking about Redrup decision?"
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 334.832,
                        "stop": 419.495,
                        "byte_start": 1413364,
                        "byte_stop": 1752016,
                        "speaker": {
                            "ID": 17862,
                            "name": "Burton Marks",
                            "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/people\/burton_marks",
                            "last_name": "Marks",
                            "roles": null,
                            "thumbnail": null,
                            "length_of_service": 0,
                            "identifier": "burton_marks"
                        },
                        "text_blocks": [
                            {
                                "start": 334.832,
                                "stop": 356.381,
                                "byte_start": 1413364,
                                "byte_stop": 1499568,
                                "text": "I am talking about Roth versus Stanley and round in the circle, back to Reidel and perhaps a little shaking of Redrup, a pinch of Redrup just to give us some, perhaps give defense attorneys a taste of heaven, again we get a Redrup decision."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 356.381,
                                "stop": 373.96,
                                "byte_start": 1499568,
                                "byte_stop": 1569890,
                                "text": "I am assuming for the purpose of this particular case that we don\u0027t have a Redrup issue because presumably this Court would decide this case on its easiest merits and that is, it\u0027s constitutionally protected as a matter of law."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 373.96,
                                "stop": 378.573,
                                "byte_start": 1569890,
                                "byte_stop": 1588385,
                                "text": "What we have here, in fact, is a very interesting proposition."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 378.573,
                                "stop": 389.272,
                                "byte_start": 1588385,
                                "byte_stop": 1631121,
                                "text": "Mr. Miller as the evidence somewhat points out, is president of incorporation which sends out advertising brochures."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 389.272,
                                "stop": 397.497,
                                "byte_start": 1631121,
                                "byte_stop": 1664035,
                                "text": "The sender of the brochures or the place where the mailings originate was Cavina, which is in the county of Los Angeles."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 397.497,
                                "stop": 417.59,
                                "byte_start": 1664035,
                                "byte_stop": 1744388,
                                "text": "In the county of Orange which is the neighboring county, a prosecution was commenced in addition to this prosecution for violation of Section 311.2 for the brochures which are illustrated history of pornography, sex orgies illustrated in the book entitled \u201cMan\/Woman.\u201d"
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 417.59,
                                "stop": 419.495,
                                "byte_start": 1744388,
                                "byte_stop": 1752016,
                                "text": "There were several prosecutions --"
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 419.495,
                        "stop": 421.29,
                        "byte_start": 1752016,
                        "byte_stop": 1759225,
                        "speaker": {
                            "ID": 15107,
                            "name": "William O. Douglas",
                            "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/people\/william_o_douglas",
                            "last_name": "Douglas",
                            "roles": [
                                {
                                    "id": 2751,
                                    "type": "scotus_justice",
                                    "date_start": -969127200,
                                    "date_end": 185004000,
                                    "appointing_president": "Franklin D. Roosevelt",
                                    "role_title": "Associate Justice of the Supreme Court of the United States",
                                    "institution_name": "Supreme Court of the United States",
                                    "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/preson_role\/scotus_justice\/2751"
                                }
                            ],
                            "thumbnail": {
                                "id": 32781,
                                "mime": "image\/png",
                                "size": 56651,
                                "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/sites\/default\/files\/william_o_douglas.png"
                            },
                            "length_of_service": 13358,
                            "identifier": "william_o_douglas"
                        },
                        "text_blocks": [
                            {
                                "start": 419.495,
                                "stop": 421.29,
                                "byte_start": 1752016,
                                "byte_stop": 1759225,
                                "text": "(Inaudible) any exhibits in this case?"
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 421.29,
                        "stop": 521.765,
                        "byte_start": 1759225,
                        "byte_stop": 2161093,
                        "speaker": {
                            "ID": 17862,
                            "name": "Burton Marks",
                            "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/people\/burton_marks",
                            "last_name": "Marks",
                            "roles": null,
                            "thumbnail": null,
                            "length_of_service": 0,
                            "identifier": "burton_marks"
                        },
                        "text_blocks": [
                            {
                                "start": 421.29,
                                "stop": 426.17,
                                "byte_start": 1759225,
                                "byte_stop": 1778765,
                                "text": "I believe they have been setup."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 426.17,
                                "stop": 439.587,
                                "byte_start": 1778765,
                                "byte_stop": 1832368,
                                "text": "These exhibits were -- and are described if you please in the opinion of Judge Arguelles in the Los Angeles Municipal Court in East Lost Angeles area."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 439.587,
                                "stop": 461.892,
                                "byte_start": 1832368,
                                "byte_stop": 1921603,
                                "text": "His description of what the material contained is at page 18 of the reporter\u0027s transcript and it repeats what -- essentially what responded his trying to hoist upon this Court that there were picture of, if you please, cunnilingus or oral copulation, sodomy, oral intercourse between a man and a woman."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 461.892,
                                "stop": 469.021,
                                "byte_start": 1921603,
                                "byte_stop": 1950128,
                                "text": "In fact, these particular pictures are drawings, artistic seems be irrelevant."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 469.021,
                                "stop": 488.368,
                                "byte_start": 1950128,
                                "byte_stop": 2027555,
                                "text": "The fact that some of them are copies of fresckles or frescoes which come from Indian art, Japanese art, also seems to be irrelevant since it becomes the job of the jury to determine under certain rules laid down whether or not they are \u201cobscene or not obscene.\u201d"
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 488.368,
                                "stop": 515.501,
                                "byte_start": 2027555,
                                "byte_stop": 2136120,
                                "text": "And also the job apparently of some experts to determine whether the average person looking at the pictures as they come to them through the mail, the average, a non-consenting adult, let\u0027s assume that that\u0027s the class we are talking about, that the average non-consenting adult upon seeing these pictures will have an immediate appeal to his prurient interest because of this exhibition."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 515.501,
                                "stop": 521.765,
                                "byte_start": 2136120,
                                "byte_stop": 2161093,
                                "text": "It doesn\u0027t seem to follow, there does not seem to be much empirical evidence and I have a red light."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 521.765,
                        "stop": 529.982,
                        "byte_start": 2161093,
                        "byte_stop": 2193903,
                        "speaker": {
                            "ID": 15073,
                            "name": "Warren E. Burger",
                            "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/people\/warren_e_burger",
                            "last_name": "Burger",
